nodes.title: SpeletGaming – Website development
nodes.content:
spēlēt.lv organizes a unique CS:GO tournament, which goal is to develop professional e-sport culture in Latvija !

Website development took a total of two weeks which includes understanding the whole project scope and development by making the website responsive on various screen resolutions.

For this project, a unique WordPress theme was created by bringing administrator rights to edit any website content or images.
